About the Author
Lara Ferroni is an author and photographer whose work has appeared in The Wall Street Journal, Imbibe Magazine, Edible Seattle,and more. Her previous books include Doughnuts, The Best Places Northwest Cookbook, Real Snacks, Popcorn and Gluten-Free Vegan Comfort Food. Lara lives in Portland, Oregon.
